<a  href="/diagrams/softlayer-vs-cloudlayer/" class="dedicated-vs-cloud left-column-button"><img src="http://static.softlayer.com/images/right-column/softlayer_vs_cloudlayer.png" alt="SoftLayer Dedicated Servers vs. CloudLayer Computing Instances.  Which would you choose?" id="softlayer_vs_cloudlayer" /></a>

<a href="/solutions/private-clouds" class="left-column-button2"><img src="http://static.softlayer.com/images/right-column/privateclouds_banner_left_nav.jpg" alt="Hig Performance Computing" style="margin-top: 15px;"/></a>
